            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27547228">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">Wie man wird, was man ist

人如何成为他所是的人？</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-12 01:01</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                Wie man wird, was man ist<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>人如何成为他所是的人？
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

